Rules for Using Commands in the Right Channels

1. No Commands in Social Chat
Social chat is for conversation only. Please avoid using bot commands here to keep the chat clean and enjoyable for everyone.


2. Use Command-Specific Channels

3. Repeated Offenses May Lead to Warnings
If you consistently use commands in the wrong channel after being reminded, you may receive a warning or timeout.


4. Accidents Happen‚ÄîJust Move It
If you accidentally use a command in social chat, no problem! Just continue the command in the correct channel.


5. Respect Everyone‚Äôs Experience
